fulltitle: Church Committee: Investigation into JFK Assassination
title: Church Committee: Investigation into JFK Assassination
description:
A short clip from the Church Committee proceedings, specifically about their investigation into the JFK killing.

Senator Schweiker (R-PA) uses the words "cover up" and "failure" to describe the behavior of the CIA and FBI towards the Warren Commission.

Senator Church (D-ID) alludes to important witnesses that couldn't be interrogated were those who turned up dead before the Church Committee could interrogate them, like two mafia members who were working with the CIA: Johnny Rosselli and Sam Giancana.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
